<%- include("header"); -%>

<div class="homecontainer">
    <div class="left-div">
        <h1>Create Your Blog</h1>
        <h3>Welcome to the World of Blogging: Unleash Your Voice, Share Your Story</h3>
        <p>In the vast landscape of the internet, there exists a realm where words weave stories, 
            ideas spark revolutions, and voices echo across the digital expanse—the world of blogging. It's more than just a platform; it's an invitation to embark on a journey of self-expression, connection, and discovery. Whether you're a seasoned wordsmith or a curious soul eager to dive into the art of blogging, this space is yours to craft, shape, and fill with the richness of your experiences. Join us as we delve into the transformative power of words, inviting you to share your unique perspective, connect with like-minded individuals, and leave an indelible mark on the digital tapestry. Blogging is not just about writing; it's about creating a conversation, leaving a legacy, and finding a community that resonates with your voice. Let the journey begin, and let your words echo through the vast corridors of the internet, inspiring and connecting in ways unimaginable. 
            This is your canvas—paint it with the hues of your thoughts, and let your story unfold.</p>
        
        
    </div>
    
    <div class="right-div">
        <img src="blogging.jpg" alt="Blogging" />
    </div>
</div>

<a href="/compose"><button>Compose New Blog</button></a>

<% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
    <div class="blog-container">
        <div class="blog-header">
            <h2>Latest Posts</h2>
            <a href="#blog-posts"><button>View All</button></a>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-posts" id="blog-posts">
            <% if (!posts) { %>
                <p>No posts available</p>
            <% } else if (posts.length === 0) { %>
                <p>No posts available</p>
            <% } else { %>
                <% for (let post of posts) { %>
                    <div class="blog-post">
                        <img src="<%= post.image %>" alt="<%= post.title %>">
                        <h3><%= post.title %></h3>
                        <p><%= post.content.substring(0, 200) + '...' %></p>
                        <a href="/posts/<%= post._id %>">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
<% } else { %>
    <div class="login-container">
        <
        <a href="login"><button>Login to View Posts</button></a>
    </div>
<% } %>






    




    












